stateDiagram-v2
    %% Project Status State Machine
    [*] --> Draft: create form
    Draft --> Created: save project
    Created --> Unassigned: enter assignment pool
    Unassigned --> WaitingForAcceptance: head assigns staff
    Unassigned --> InProgress: staff self-picks job
    WaitingForAcceptance --> InProgress: staff accepts
    WaitingForAcceptance --> Unassigned: staff declines or head changes assignee
    InProgress --> Returned: head returns for correction
    Returned --> InProgress: staff resubmits
    InProgress --> ProcurementCompleted: all procurement steps completed
    ProcurementCompleted --> AssetCheck: prompt asset code check
    AssetCheck --> ContractManagement: continue to contract phase
    ContractManagement --> Completed: contract work completed
    Created --> CancellationPending: cancellation requested
    Unassigned --> CancellationPending: cancellation requested
    WaitingForAcceptance --> CancellationPending: cancellation requested
    InProgress --> CancellationPending: cancellation requested
    ContractManagement --> CancellationPending: cancellation requested
    CancellationPending --> Cancelled: head approves
    CancellationPending --> InProgress: head rejects during procurement
    CancellationPending --> ContractManagement: head rejects during contract phase
    Completed --> [*]
    Cancelled --> [*]
